OL,5, A Holocaust survivor says she is "so   
OL,6, touched" to receive a letter from King 
OL,7, Charles to honour her 100th birthday.  
OL,9,FThree years ago, Lily Ebert's story    
OL,10,Fwent viral as she searched for the     
OL,11,Ffamily of the American soldier who     
OL,12,Fliberated her from the Auschwitz       
OL,13,Fconcentration camp.                    
OL,15,FThe King praised her "extraordinary    
OL,16,Fstrength of spirit, resilience, and    
OL,17,Fcourage".                              
OL,19,FHe also sent Ms Ebert flowers as he    
OL,20,Fmarked the "very special occasion".    
